{"image_id": "ADS_2009_page_213", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "ALLIANCE DATA SYSTEMS CORPORATION", "bbox": [392.8, 140.2, 832.8, 161.0]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS—(Continued)", "bbox": [273.2, 177.7, 952.4, 198.5]}, {"text": "portion of the grant-date fair value of the original award for which the requisite service period was rendered at", "bbox": [137.6, 227.9, 1058.5, 248.8]}, {"text": "the date of cancellation plus the incremental cost resulting from the cancellation and replacement.", "bbox": [137.6, 252.9, 954.2, 273.8]}, {"text": "In March 2009, the Company determined that it was no longer probable that the specified performance", "bbox": [179.2, 301.6, 1037.2, 322.4]}, {"text": "measures associated with certain performance-based restricted stock units would be achieved. As a result,", "bbox": [137.6, 326.6, 1020.7, 347.4]}, {"text": "1,242,098 performance-based restricted stock units granted during 2008 and January 2009 having a weighted-", "bbox": [137.6, 351.6, 1056.2, 372.4]}, {"text": "average grant date fair value of $56.43 per share, are no longer probable to vest. The Company did not", "bbox": [137.6, 376.6, 993.7, 397.5]}, {"text": "recognized stock-based compensation expense related to those awards no longer probable to vest.", "bbox": [137.6, 401.6, 952.1, 422.5]}, {"text": "Stock Options", "bbox": [137.6, 462.0, 257.5, 482.8]}, {"text": "Stock option awards are granted with an exercise price equal to the market price of the Company’s stock on", "bbox": [179.2, 498.9, 1079.1, 519.8]}, {"text": "the date of grant. Options typically vest ratably over three years and expire ten years after the date of grant. The", "bbox": [137.6, 524.0, 1070.1, 544.8]}, {"text": "fair value of each option award is estimated on the date of grant using a binomial lattice model.", "bbox": [137.6, 549.0, 933.3, 569.8]}, {"text": "No stock option awards were granted during the years ended December 31, 2009 and 2008. During the ye